sp.p:
Marie, Marie!    (she shrieks and breaks from him, flying to her father's door, R.;
      Lascelles seizes her hand, and as she stands trembling between her contending feelings, the
      curtain descends)

I dare say there is. Come through this room—it opens on my garden. And so you are going to
       France, eh? Well, now, how very odd—for, do you know, you've never paid up your two shares;
       so, whilst I send a boy down to the beach to enquire, you can hand me the difference.
